text: Orlando Chavarria (born 31 July 1971) is a Belizean former cyclist. He competed in the team time trial at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1971 births Category:Living people Category:Belizean male cyclists Category:Cyclists at the 1994 Commonwealth Games Category:Commonwealth Games competitors for Belize Category:Olympic cyclists of Belize Category:Cyclists at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
